                        "id": "55e85678-ce04-4b1a-8ae6-1ba164d60384",
                        "exerciseName": "Full lips",
                        "exerciseDescription": "<p><strong>Massage of the circular muscle of the mouth</strong></p><p>Do you want your lips to become plump? Then this is the right exercise for you!<br>But it is more than just for beautiful and full lips. This exercise tones the circular muscle of the mouth, which has a positive effect on the general appearance of the mouth.</p><p>Please remember that the rejuvenation is a complex process. So, leaving out a part of the face unattended can upset the dynamics of the process as a whole, even if you don&rsquo;t see the effect right away.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Caution:</strong> You work on the muscle (orbicularis muscle of the mouth), not on the lips, although you should also pay attention to the lips, especially at their relaxed state.</p><p>Check out what muscles you will work on</p><p><span class=\"fr-video fr-deletable fr-fvc fr-dvb fr-draggable\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"true\"><iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/543684139\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"fr-draggable\"></iframe></span><br></p><p><strong>Technique</strong><br>- Clamp the corners of your lips, in their usual position, with the outer edge or the base of your palms. Press them to the teeth. They should not slip out of this grip.<br>- Purse your lips forward and form them in a bell shape. At the same time, the border of your lips should be relaxed. Hold it for up to 1 minute.<br>- If you are aiming for beautiful lips, you can repeat the exercise up to 5 times a day.</p><p>Attention!<br>When you purse out your lips, you should constantly remember that the border of the lips must be relaxed. It is not always that easy to learn this right away. Go for it!&nbsp;</p><p>Luscious kisses to you! <span class=\"fr-emoticon fr-deletable fr-emoticon-img\" style=\"background: url(https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/emojione/2.0.1/assets/svg/1f609.svg);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br><em>Good luck! <span class=\"fr-emoticon fr-deletable fr-emoticon-img\" style=\"background: url(https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/emojione/2.0.1/assets/svg/1f60c.svg);\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</em></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>",
